  "text": "Created a comprehensive README.md for the door agent sprite generator. Covered all major aspects: installation, usage, customization, technical details, and practical examples. The README makes the project accessible to both end users who just want to generate sprites and developers who want to modify or extend the system. Included working HTML/CSS examples and Python snippets for analyzing the generated data. The documentation matches the current codebase functionality perfectly.",
